            <title>【2012.2.9 夜】个股炒作低调疯狂</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_453151380102duxe.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font STYLE="FonT-siZe: 32px; FonT-FAMiLY: Times new roman"><em>&nbsp;
【2012.2.9 夜】个股炒作低调疯狂</EM></FONT></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#0D20FD">风来疏竹，风过而竹不留声；</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#0D20FD">雁度寒潭，雁去而潭不留影。</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#0D20FD">故君子事来而心始现，事去而心随空。</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#0D20FD">气象要高旷，而不可疏狂。心思要缜缄，而不可琐屑。</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#0D20FD">趣味要冲淡，而不可偏枯。操守要严明，而不可激烈。</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#0D20FD">——————————————————————————————————————————</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p><font STYLE="FonT-siZe: 14px" SIZE="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
开年到现在，大盘股指只是蜗牛一般爬升了两百来点，但是很多个股炒作主力却都收获的盆满钵满。第一波是以ST为标志；第二波是以有色之中的锌业股份、罗平锌电等小金属为主的有色炒作。大盘没有走多高，但是这些个股动辄最低是50%高的甚至达到了翻番的涨幅。这样的个股行情，超出很多人预料。</FONT></P>
<p>&nbsp;<a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s14.sinaimg.cn/orignal/45315138hb882d99a248d" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://s14.sinaimg.cn/middle/45315138hb882d99a248d&amp;690" WIDTH="690" HEIGHT="460" NAME="image_operate_79331328772068430" /></A></P>
<br />
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;
为什么会出现这样的结构性不动声色炒作？还是各路游资主力所为。公募基金汇金险资不动，但是这些江湖各路私募和游资主力们反倒露出嗜血的本性，疯狂突击。比如这两天的宇顺电子。这就要求中小资金不要太过于关注大盘走势，多花点时间找找这样的牛股。那才是你的真命天子。</P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
有色小金属的炒作，将会如羞答答玫瑰静悄悄开一样，逐步蔓延渗透到其它如铜、镍、稀土、锑、钽、铝等题材。对于前期已经涨幅过高的锌金属个股，不要追高，主力资金必然高位出货尔后再突击一直横盘的个股。你要做的就是提前布局。</P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s3.sinaimg.cn/orignal/45315138h78d9e2e006a2" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://s3.sinaimg.cn/middle/45315138h78d9e2e006a2&amp;690" WIDTH="690" HEIGHT="460" NAME="image_operate_41131328772334749" /></A></P>
<br />
<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
盘面上，目前的板块轮动速度和频率过快，今天盘中放量，但是获利盘了结落袋资金为主。明天周末，按照这样的板块轮动趋势和频率，可以关注下三低个股中的水泥、农林牧渔、小金属和化工、医药。个人观点，据此入市，风险自负。</P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
