<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#2251FE">教人以善毋过高，当使其可从。</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#2251FE">见一善行，窃以济私；</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
<font COLOR="#2251FE">闻一善言，假以覆短。是又藉寇兵而赍盗粮矣。</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="WorD-spACinG: 0px; FonT: 14px/24px nsimsun; TexT-TrAnsForM: none; CoLor: rgb(0,0,0); TexT-inDenT: 0px; WHiTe-spACe: normal; LeTTer-spACinG: normal; BACKGroUnD-CoLor: rgb(255,255,255); webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">
